  stimulus_text = 'The author''s main goal in the passage is to describe the features of a new product—a special type of food that is being promoted as a healthy and delicious alternative to traditional snacks. The author claims that the product is made with all-natural ingredients, and that it is a source of essential vitamins and minerals. The author also states that the product is available in several flavors. Which of the following sentences should be added to the end of the passage to most effectively conclude the argument?',
